value.0:
This stone seems to resonate with immense divine energy. As you place your hand around it, you get a mental image of a familiar temple.

Though, you feel a sense of foreboding and loss as you handle the stone. You feel your very coin purse jingle, as well as a sense of forgetfulness.

Activating this stone should bring you back to the temple you last attuned with, but likely with some loss of experience and gold.
